title: Unidentified
content:
Unidentified may refer to:

  • Unidentified fossils, found whilst performing various activities on Fossil Island.
    • Unidentified small fossil
    • Unidentified medium fossil
    • Unidentified large fossil
    • Unidentified rare fossil
  • Unidentified fragments, found whilst performing various activities within the Shattered Relics League.
  • Unidentified liquid, a liquid that the archaeological expert needs to identify.
  • Unidentified minerals, found whilst mining in the members-only area of the Mining Guild.
  • Grimy herbs, prior to an update.
